Status: FAILURE

Followup: Scheduled

Images:http://imgur.com/a/5Eadd

Summary: Skylab is the pride and joy of Republic of Aristotzkan Kerbals. Using KOSMOS parts and Nova Punch engines it is efficient as well as sci-ency! Today's mission is to dock the brand new (and shiny) laboratory, 3 kerbonauts will be tagging along and will resupply the existing station with toothpas- er um, astronaut food. But disaster strikes as the Skylab breaks apart. No crew is hurt and a recovery mission is scheduled and will have a follow up post.
